metadata.name: Tom Yum Carnival 2022
metadata.description:
My first collection is Pictures of fun mixed with diversity. From the imagination of happiness due to the celebration of many characters. through the form of a menu called Tom Yum, which is part of one of the cultural traditions of Thailand This menu is one thing that people in the world know and love. Appreciate this unique flavor as well.

The workflow starts from The idea was to present an image of a carnival where people gathered to celebrate on the streets. have cooking setting up shop kiosks There are various activities filled with happiness

From the sketch, create a piece with Adobe Illustrator. Size 7,680 x 4,320 pixels 40 layers

Work began in November 2021 and was completed in early February 2022.

I hope that those who have touched this work will feel the endless increase in imagination and have great happiness 

Finally, I will give you a digitally printed piece, size 70 x 120 cm, nicely framed. with the winning bidder
